This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing and topic modeling. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) because topic modeling is often used in information retrieval tasks. Additionally, the paper discusses user control and evaluation of HLTM systems, which could fall under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper also touches on human-computer interaction, which could place it in the sub-category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
